{"tid":1566432,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"JYP又有女團成員宣布離開！","createTime":"2019-09-13T14:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T03:31:55.000Z","uid":74065,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f4821b5591c28770e73d6369914368f3441123b1","tid":1566432,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"南韓JYP娛樂捧紅TWICE、GOT7等偶像團體，但美聲團體卻聲勢不足，2012年推出雙人女團15&amp;，由白藝潾與朴智敏組成，繼後者離巢後，稍早白藝潾也在IG提前1天宣布，要和從國小至今待了12年的公司說再見！<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4370/d4370183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4370%2Fd4370183.jpg&h=5ebe291f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲待12年少女歌手白藝潾確定不續約。（圖／翻攝自yerin_the_genuine IG）<br />\n<br />\n白藝潾在IG上表示，和JYP的合約將於明（14）日到期，她從國小10歲開始進入公司，至今已經過了12年，特別感謝「有時候像父母、有時候像老師與監護人一起長時間努力的社長朴軫永（JYP）」但現在去除旗下藝人與社長的關係之後，兩人依舊維持好感情，她表示，「說好了之後以摯友身分相處」。<br />\n<br />\n她還透露未來動向，將會創立自己的獨立品牌，讓不少粉絲感慨，「不管在哪都會永遠支持你」，而她的PO文也立馬吸引知名製作人CHANGMO、Code Kunst在下面留言應援。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2670/d2670280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2670%2Fd2670280.jpg&h=64427d35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲白藝潾（右）和朴智敏曾組15&amp;出道。（圖／翻攝自15&amp;官方臉書）<br />\n<br />\n22歲的白藝潾，7年前與選秀節目《Kpop Star》第一季冠軍朴智敏組成15&amp;，但被認為不若偶像般的外貌，也不走動感舞曲路線，目前只發行過一張正規專輯以及4張單曲，接下來兩人幾乎都採個人分頭活動。繼上個月朴智敏與JYP合約到期、宣布解約之後，15&amp;等於解散，然後白藝潾現在也宣布單飛，確定離開住了她青春10多年的老東家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經數唔到一年走左幾多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b1c36e4213613a6883f95f1434cc6cf7ea3d11","tid":1566432,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"91c210c332ead0026651f0170b199f05d73da359","tid":1566432,"uid":213300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:45:06.000Z","msg":"唉yerin合約到期<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f87abe5433c9ed927022306f1871b0dc7cc5ac","tid":1566432,"uid":149371,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"牙導中秋都不忘JYP<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f203d774c4e4c1adb0f2762c7241100ba4caaf6","tid":1566432,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f87abe5433c9ed927022306f1871b0dc7cc5ac","tid":1566432,"uid":149371,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"牙導中秋都不忘JYP<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"我的心每分每刻 仍然被他佔有"},{"pid":"e77c13c883e0698092e29e81f720f359e44efd49","tid":1566432,"uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f203d774c4e4c1adb0f2762c7241100ba4caaf6","tid":1566432,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f87abe5433c9ed927022306f1871b0dc7cc5ac","tid":1566432,"uid":149371,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:45:23.000Z","msg":"牙導中秋都不忘JYP<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:50:55.000Z","msg":"我的心每分每刻 仍然被他佔有"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T14:52:51.000Z","msg":"我佔有JYP肉體<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" cla